content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #93804 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
I'd consider P-high, just because it seems like it would be hard for an end user to figure out what's going on.

I'd also say more in the p-medium zone.
I'd also like a smaller reproducer for this, it may even be a cumulative effect of many impl traits in that codebase (but it might not be so easy to reduce while staying reproducible)
